{"article_id":"P4aEgznK86DFKAJD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Former FBI director James Comey has said","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Donald Trump is `` morally unfit","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"to be president ''","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"and treats women like `` pieces of meat '' .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Mr Comey was giving his first major television interview","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"since he was fired by President Trump last year .","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"He told ABC News","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"that Mr Trump lies constantly","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"and may have obstructed justice .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Hours before the interview aired ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"the president went on the offensive ,","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"accusing Mr Comey of `` many lies '' .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Mr Comey told ABC 's 20/20 programme on Sunday night :","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"`` I do n't buy this stuff about him being mentally incompetent or early stages of dementia . ''","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"he 's medically unfit","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"to be president .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"I think","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"he 's morally unfit","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"to be president .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"`` Our president must embody respect","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"and adhere to the values","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"that are at the core of this country .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"The most important being truth .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"This president is not able to do that , ''","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr Comey said .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"After the interview aired ,","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Mr Trump 's party","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"- via the Republican National Committee -","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"released a statement","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"Mr Comey 's publicity tour for his new book showed","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"`` his true higher loyalty is to himself '' .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"`` The only thing worse than Comey 's history of misconduct is his willingness","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"to say anything","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"to sell books , ''","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"it said .","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"It is the latest development in a long-standing feud between the two men ,","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"further fuelled by the upcoming publication of Mr Comey 's memoir A Higher Loyalty :","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"Truth , Lies and Leadership .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"The ex-FBI chief is on a publicity blitz for the book .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"President Trump has said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"the `` badly reviewed book '' raises `` big questions '' .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"He also suggested","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"Mr Comey should be imprisoned ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and in recent days began referring to him as a `` slime ball '' .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"The story dates back to the 2016 presidential election ,","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"when Mr Comey was FBI director ,","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"and the investigation into Democrat candidate Hillary Clinton 's handling of classified emails on a private server while Secretary of State .","depth":4},{"id":49,"text":"In July 2016 , he said","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"that she had been `` extremely careless '' in her handling of the emails ,","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"but the FBI would not press charges .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"However , in October , days before the vote , he sent a letter to Congress","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"telling them","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"the FBI was reopening an investigation","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"after finding more emails .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"The letter went public","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"- and Mrs Clinton says","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"it handed Donald Trump the election .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"On 6 November , the FBI said","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"it had completed its review into the new trove of emails","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and there would , again , be no charges .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"Once Mr Trump became president ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Mr Comey says","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"he tried to extract a pledge of personal loyalty from him","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"- something","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"the president fiercely denies .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"In March 2017 ,","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"when alleged links between Mr Trump 's campaign and Russia were being investigated by the FBI ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"Mr Trump allegedly pressured Mr Comey to publicly declare","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that the president was not personally being investigated - something","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"the then director says","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"he declined to do .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Some Democrats blamed Mr Comey for costing Mrs Clinton the election ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"while Trump supporters felt","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"he was targeting the president with the Russia investigation .","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Before revealing the new Clinton investigation ,","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"one staff member asked Mr Comey :","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"`` Should you consider","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"that what you 're about do to may help elect Donald Trump president ? ''","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Mr Comey said","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"he responded :","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"`` Down that path lies the death of the FBI as an independent force . ''","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"On the Clinton probe more generally , he said :","depth":6},{"id":84,"text":"`` The FBI drove this investigation","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"and we did it in a competent and independent way .","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"I would bet my life on that . ''","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"He was fired by President Trump in May","depth":6},{"id":88,"text":"and found out about his dismissal","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"by watching TV news .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"ABC News has released a full 42,000-word transcript of the interview between Mr Comey and chief anchor George Stephanopoulos .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"A chunk of the interview deals with the sacking of National Security Adviser Michael Flynn on 13 February 2017","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"for lying about contacts with the Russian ambassador .","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"A day later , Mr Comey is sitting in the Oval Office with Mr Trump alone","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"- the vice-president and the attorney-general have been asked to leave .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"The former FBI head asserts in the interview","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"that Mr Trump tried to pressure him into dropping any investigation into Mr Flynn .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"`` I took it as a direction , ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"he told Mr Stephanopoulos .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"`` He 's -","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"his words were , though ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"' I hope you can let it go ' . ''","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"Mr Comey says","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"he let the comment pass ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"but concedes","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"he should perhaps have suggested to the president","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"that it would amount to obstruction of justice .","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"`` It 's certainly some evidence of obstruction of justice .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"It would depend","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"- and I 'm just a witness in this case , not the investigator or prosecutor ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"it would depend upon other things","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that reflected on his intent . ''","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"James Comey thinks","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"Donald Trump is a serial liar","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"who degrades women","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"and is `` morally unfit '' to be president .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"He says","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"it 's `` possible '' but `` unlikely '' that Russia has compromised the president ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"and that he may have obstructed the collusion investigation .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"He also believes","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"the American people ca n't do anything about it until the November 2020 presidential election .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"That 's just one of the contradictions","depth":7},{"id":122,"text":"that emerged in Mr Comey 's interview .","depth":7},{"id":123,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"he strove to make non-political decisions about the highly political 2016 investigations into Hillary Clinton and the Trump campaign .","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"He spoke of integrity and honour ,","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"but confessed","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"that he may not have had the `` guts ''","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"to confront the president .","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"The former director gave a complex interview","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"reflecting a man","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"challenged to draw meaning from his place at the centre of the biggest political stories of a lifetime .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"It made for gripping television .","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"Now Trump loyalists will pick apart his remarks","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"and return fire .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"`` Nobody gets out alive , ''","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Mr Comey quipped in the early days of the Clinton investigation .","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"It was n't really a joke then .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"And it certainly is n't now .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"In the primetime TV interview , Mr Comey suggested","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"that the president had surrounded himself with people loyal to him","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"- he compared Mr Trump to mob bosses","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"he had investigated as a prosecutor .","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"`` The loyalty oaths , the boss as the dominant centre of everything ,","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"it 's all about how do you serve the boss , what 's in the boss ' interests , ''","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"Asked if those around the president were `` enabling bad behaviour '' ,","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"Mr Comey said :","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"`` The challenge of this president is that he will stain everyone around him . ''","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"Mr Comey , however , said","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"he did not believe","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"President Trump should be impeached .","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"`` I hope not","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"because I think","depth":14},{"id":154,"text":"impeaching and removing Donald Trump from office would let the American people off the hook , ''","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"he said .","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Instead ,","depth":13},{"id":157,"text":"he said ,","depth":13},{"id":158,"text":"it was something","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"the American people were `` duty-bound to do directly '' at the voting booth .","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":319,"left":205,"right":318,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":185,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":168,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":168,"left":165,"right":167,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":165,"left":163,"right":164,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":0,"right":162,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":162,"left":161,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":161,"left":1,